Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:56.88,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}一同化為塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:10.04,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}現在只不過是想帶著悲傷的夢來旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:15.60,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}明明陪在你身邊 用盡全力卻也沒有實現
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.86,0:26:21.42,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}解開冰冷的心 鮮血卻一直流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.70,0:26:24.50,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}我將一直留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.68,0:26:27.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}一直緊跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.56,0:26:32.09,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}當我們乘上光之船
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.27,0:26:37.57,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}那起風時的音符 將會奏響
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.11,0:25:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.96,0:25:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.26,0:25:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 為什麼禁忌的這個名字會…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.66,0:25:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 搞什麼 這個合體
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.33,0:25:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 以前從來沒有過這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 Aquarion是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.19,0:25:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 多納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不行 只要威瑟石還存在 禁斷的男女合體…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以往的常識和感覺都四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.04,0:25:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四分五裂地爆裂開
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.89,0:26:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂了 一直珍藏的某種東西 爆發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.26,0:26:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這個形態
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 進化了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.17,0:26:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新計數器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.87,0:26:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣久違的 臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以新的姿態出現的禁斷名字
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.90,0:26:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.53,0:26:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終焉將如期而至 現在即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.94,0:27:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然說Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.36,0:27:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦漿在顫動
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.60,0:27:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預料之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.32,0:27:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就將你們變成灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.25,0:27:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個氣味的真正面目是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.19,0:27:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷的Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以Vector Z為頭部的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.09,0:27:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion竟然還有別的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的不潔 男女合體應該是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.17,0:27:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.51,0:27:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由那些少年們的手裡解開
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.78,0:27:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是在Aquarion的裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.39,0:27:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.84,0:27:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快從那個男人身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.63,0:27:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶走並駕駛Aquarion的恐怖分子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.36,0:27:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.15,0:27:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君不是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.52,0:27:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要狡辯了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.59,0:28:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來了 普通人的組合來當頭部什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.51,0:28:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官 司令部傳來的強制合體解除要求
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.35,0:28:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就在試了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.89,0:28:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.65,0:28:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.23,0:28:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊的控制一切都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.79,0:28:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然跟那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.31,0:28:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.12,0:28:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園長　啊不 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.35,0:28:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.59,0:28:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同於現在的Aquaria樣的男女分開的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是雌雄同體的勝利之完全體
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 神的道具人類怎麼能夠使用
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.97,0:28:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊這個傢伙  虛有其表嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.40,0:28:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出真正的實力上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.67,0:29:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.91,0:29:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要 沒辦法的 戰鬥什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.95,0:29:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不要這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.39,0:29:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被勉強進來的 出去也是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.56,0:29:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 少女 這種狀況你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.56,0:29:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君 逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.74,0:29:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為「我們都是廢柴什麼的」
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.47,0:29:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.03,0:29:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.37,0:29:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方的增援
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.74,0:29:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子不是雜魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型機 同型號的三台
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.75,0:29:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊你們
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂大人 有回艦命令
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.54,0:29:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請和我們一起回Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.26,0:29:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲那個老頭子的指使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.73,0:30:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Neagula的採取已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.33,0:30:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這之後的戰鬥是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.18,0:30:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定是否戰鬥的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.04,0:30:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是等著被幹掉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.84,0:30:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好了 我來教你戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.69,0:30:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將拉手上的鎖解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.77,0:30:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.55,0:30:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.26,0:30:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡的Element能力異常地增幅了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.06,0:30:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個小鬼共鳴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.73,0:30:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是男女機合體
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.28,0:30:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同 和以往的Aquaria完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.81,0:31:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神 神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.35,0:31:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這群傢伙是來拖後腿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.94,0:31:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不需要你來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.64,0:31:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.77,0:31:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.77,0:31:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味 氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.55,0:31:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味的盡頭 有黑暗伴隨
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.20,0:31:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把別的機體的部分強硬地接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.53,0:31:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣還有那種動作
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.62,0:31:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝過野獸的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.54,0:31:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.09,0:31:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.54,0:31:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的不要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.87,0:31:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊 這個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.48,0:31:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就一直哭個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.46,0:31:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是戰鬥中 別分神 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.47,0:32:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.11,0:32:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 能保護得了她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.03,0:32:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.91,0:32:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.23,0:32:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喪服的結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.27,0:32:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做過的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.34,0:32:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結 結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.87,0:32:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element能力 絕望之血
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.90,0:32:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的影像刺激到腦部
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.66,0:32:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個場景為什麼我們能看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.78,0:32:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.43,0:32:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回禁斷之名的Aquarion展示給我們看的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.96,0:32:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預知到的是這樣的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.56,0:32:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕望而最糟的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.24,0:32:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那裡的是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.54,0:32:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.16,0:32:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁邊的男人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.00,0:32:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把臉給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.09,0:33:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.09,0:33:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.97,0:33:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣味的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.11,0:33:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.80,0:33:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是你的錯 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.14,0:33:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行胡亂的合體 還牽扯進御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.24,0:34:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你這混蛋的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.18,0:34:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 心跳加快 興奮不止
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.42,0:34:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小一直被大家避諱著
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那人置於不顧也是 這力量的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.77,0:34:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 決定不再使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.27,0:34:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想要保護御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.10,0:34:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.37,0:34:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻讓御子乃經歷更加糟糕的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.47,0:34:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這種人 要保護御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.70,0:34:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.53,0:34:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.55,0:34:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.76,0:34:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.53,0:34:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屏障等級低下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.21,0:35:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去Aquarion會…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.57,0:35:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被神話認可
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.64,0:35:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是自身成為神話
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.05,0:35:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔·空 你已擁有這份覺悟了嗎
